IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User lewinkoon@gmail.com
Passcmd "pass email/personal"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/inbox

Channel gmail-inbox
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :gmail-local:sent

Channel gmail-draft
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :gmail-local:draft

Channel gmail-trash
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :gmail-local:trash

Channel gmail-university
Master :gmail-remote:university
Slave :gmail-local:university

Channel gmail-notifications
Master :gmail-remote:notifications
Slave :gmail-local:notifications

Channel gmail-archive
Master :gmail-remote:keep
Slave :gmail-local:archive

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-draft
Channel gmail-trash
Channel gmail-notifications
Channel gmail-university
Channel gmail-archive

Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
